name: No Time (itch) (G̸l̸i̷t̴c̶h̸e̵d̵ ̷J̶s̵o̷n̴)
description:
I really want to participate, but I have no time. Still having exams right now...
And, as a responsible adult, I just spent 4 hours out of my 72, making a game for a game jam, instead of actually studying!

Anyway, made in four hours for the GMTK game jam, here's No Time cause that's what I have right now, Enjoy!
